OL,4,CAndrew Lloyd Webber rejects PM's offer
OL,5,Cfor Cinderella to be Covid pilot
OL,6, Andrew Lloyd Webber has rejected Prime
OL,7, Minister Boris Johnson's offer to add
OL,8, his new musical Cinderella to a pilot
OL,9, scheme for full-capacity live events.
OL,11,FThe PM said earlier this week he was in
OL,12,Ftalks with the theatre impresario.
OL,14,FBut Lord Lloyd-Webber said on Friday
OL,15,Fthe theatre industry had been treated
OL,16,Fas "an afterthought and undervalued".
OL,18,FLast week, he said he was determined to
OL,19,Fopen his show to a full house on 25
OL,20,FJune, even if he risked being arrested.
OL,21,FHowever, he has now rowed back on that.
